{"tid":504760,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"西九戲曲中心地盤20工人追薪 佔領馬路拉橫額","createTime":"2017-12-20T11:28:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-21T14:09:11.000Z","uid":62599,"like":21,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"796ef768b1b9979abb236444d2804cb0c0856899","tid":504760,"uid":62599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T11:28:14.000Z","msg":"西九文化區發生追薪事件，下午4時許，約20名工人於西九戲曲中心地盤外抗議，聲稱向公司追討久薪，其中10人情緒激動，衝出廣東道拉橫額，阻擋行車，數部巴士途經被逼停下。警員接報趕至，將衝出馬路的工人帶回行人路，並聯絡勞工處協助。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，被拖糧的工人是鋁板裝工，聲稱9月時公司已遲出糧，上月更冇糧出，拖欠30名工人合共約200萬工資。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20171220/57606568\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171220%2F57606568&d=Xd07no4XomrZPhsnyzK6ar%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=3fa1fb92\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171220%2F57606568&h=379c20e1\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20171220/57606568</a>"},{"pid":"2f3d8915344ffb9fd1a1b0156c66e74b50347082","tid":504760,"uid":55043,"like":36,"dislike":0,"score":36,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T11:33:38.000Z","msg":"拉布冇工開<br />\n<br />\n唔拉布有工開<br />\n<br />\n不過冇糧出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2074ca0118b491d884dd449b7a017e029cb9c758","tid":504760,"uid":79632,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T11:36:47.000Z","msg":"總之阻人返工就唔啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c16ca0bd6974921acc6caa3d6f055c346e3f06f","tid":504760,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T11:40:11.000Z","msg":"勞工處職員：不如七折出糧啦<br />\n(設計對白）"},{"pid":"6c1e2ec100e31352f96043b655c474e72cf66ff6","tid":504760,"uid":41116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T11:41:56.000Z","msg":"地盤真係好好揾"},{"pid":"f34ebc